Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Otonashi. Ah, the editor? \NTranscribing Miss Teresa's tape right now. Almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all alright. I'll be done in no time. \NSo, if you excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The first-class pianist enjoys pachislot in her free time. Ain't that peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Teresa, what are your \Npersonal sensations towards pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As I told you before, I believe that the piano rhythm \Nand the pachislot rhythm are the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has their own unique approach to pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.63,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Do you think otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa plays the machines \Nas though they are piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi treats the machines as human beings, \Ninspecting and talking to pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In pachislot, there are truly as many ways to play as there are men. This game is {\i1}that{\i0} profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone strives to reach the pinnacle of pachislot-mastery.\NAnd the one occupying this pinnacle now is Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Finger of God wielder \Nand a man who perfected the pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I must, at any cost, rise to Daiba Ryo's level \Nto show him once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, what am I doing? I have to finish in time \Nto make it to Teresa's extra concert with Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what if you master pachislot too well? \NWhat then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I truly master it, \Neven death will no longer frighten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:50.82,Default,,0,0,2,,{\fade(900,900)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad2\blur0.5\3c&H6D5B95&\4c&H55397C&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H41&\fscx117\fscy88}Episode 5 \N {\fs86}Future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, is Yuri around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's off to Miss Teresa's extra concert with Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, seeing her concert in person \Nis terrific every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think! Her music is so good \Nat making women cry. It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, thanks for inviting me. \NI'll return that after I wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no problem at all. \NAre you going to the gym now? I can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the subway will do it faster. \NThanks for everything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,While being serious and courteous, \Nshe remains tender and sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Patience, Oumi! \NFor a first date, it's a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, too late after all? \NWait though... Oumi should be on a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still catch them in the parking lot! Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Teresa, where are you planning to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is America.\NAfter that I'm going to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that in your spare time \Nyou like to play pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My... So you already know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I not be interested in something else besides music?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since combined, \Nthose two activities create a great symphony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Every pachislot reel has exactly 21 title on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there are 3 of these reels, it's easy to calculate - \Nthe total possible number of combinations is over 9,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting the whole ensemble to play in one rhythm is tricky, \Nbut isn't it a great way to hit the Big?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...Or a great way to play a concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, pachislot is kind of cultural leisure \Nthat pleases the hearts of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pachislot is a cultural leisure{\i0} you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ginya! Did you come to see the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, I didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. \NI'm still glad we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeming pachislot a kind of a cultural leisure is a good point. I'll add it to my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I expect you to write a good article.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, you aren't upset about losing to me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, it was embarrassing.\NBut for some reason, I also felt refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it helped you to refresh? \NUp for a revenge already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! We'll definitely do it \Nthe next time you are in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you press the buttons and the way you write your articles radiate the same kind of ardor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost certain, if you'd play more from your feelings, \NI would've had much harder times winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that time, you were too astounded by my way of pressing the buttons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,never managing to regain your own rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It heated you further up, \Ncausing you to rush and make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of his inability to catch neither the rhythm of the waves nor the rhythm of the machine, Ginya lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you must not forget - that ardor of yours is bound to become an incredible weapon later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to our next meeting. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! \NWhat is it between you and Teresa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your claims on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's... \NWe just played pachislot once, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you! What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly gave Yuri a ride to the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium's call!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The promotion game between the four members begins shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting score - 200 coins.\NThe first one to score 2000, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4... 3... 2... 1... Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That young man made it to the fourth round after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Otonashi Ginya? \NI wonder if he wins and gets promoted to knight today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me \Nthat the miniskirt will seize the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...\NUltimate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, since the appearance of this newcomer, I see him much more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should not forget - your ardor is bound to become \Nan incredibly powerful weapon later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush... Otherwise,\NI'll miss a good chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Riichi is on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses guy got carried away \Nand lost concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Another Big for the miniskirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The rookie is completely out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Before hitting at least one Big, \Nhe'll run out of coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you had played using your feelings, \NI would have not won that easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at that time, you were too astonished with my way of pressing the buttons, failing to regain your own rhythm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That heated you further up, \Nmaking you hurry and make mistakes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush... Calm down! \NRhythm... My own rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Rhythm. My own rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. The winner is Otonashi Ginya. \NFinal score is 2014 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit some pretty good Bigs today. \NHowever, it was a no way to press the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you abuse luck, it will run out very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Gin, I'm pleased to see you heeded my recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow at 1 PM..." \NWhat could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This place belongs to one of my good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero to latest - \Nmachines of all generations presented here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not Daiba's collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't collect things myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be anything but slotter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For a slotter, pachislot machine \Nshould not exceed the mean of playing and having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's the approach you developed \Nthrough the years of playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not enjoying it the way a usual fan would. \NIt helps to remain collected in the heat of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you intend to be a successful slotter in Slothium, \Nyou need to know the secrets of the pachislot machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing the mechanics and history \Nis not barely enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the slotter's heart is filthy, \Nfilthy is his game," isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, \Nthat's one impressive collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Found something interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing of the kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in this machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall right, \Nonly three of those were assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It has never been in use, never seen the light of a parlor. \NIt's a ghost machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost... machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of inventive and creative designers \Ntook part in creating it. It was devised with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet not a single Parlor ever exhibited one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba, aren't we playing one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the pachislot machines are being collected. \NWe can find a better place for playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your method of pushing buttons has a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flaw?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You play pachislot with a feeling of deep hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hatred?{\i0} On the contrary, I'm sort of addicted to pachislot! It makes my blood boil! But the hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Being agitated while playing is normal. \NIt's just that you sometimes manifest other emotions too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In Slothium you always play as though you are throwing yourself off a high cliff into the raging sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You face this sea and its endless stream of cruel waves head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to prevail through force and persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just really want to win. \NIs it wrong thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, this cruel sea \Nwill mercilessly crush you against the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A sandy beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This beach is the antipode \Nof the cliff you're jumping off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of fighting the cruel sea, \Nthe beach plays with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He gently meets the waves lashing him, \Nand then turns them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NBut there's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How the slotter acts in such situations \Ndepends on his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Depends on the heart{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to the game center?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with game center pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that only kids play it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot in the game center allows everyone \Nto genuinely enjoy this game to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the parlor machines\Nhave somewhat harder settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one more measure \Nto make it the most enjoyable for visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone does whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really playing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How inconsistent of you. Aren't you the one \Ncraving to fight me again, regardless the conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. But there are reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to business then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I meant in Slothium!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning to ever fight you in Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Slothium or the game center, \Nisn't it all the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still willing to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The initial score is 500 coins.\NThe first one to hit the Big, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In Slothium, he may be the Ultimate King.\NBut here and now, Daiba is the ordinary slotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba... Even in a place like this, \Nhe remains collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes my first Small Factor.\NI won't miss this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a game center pachislot! \NI can't let myself be defeated here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are constantly rushing head-on, \Nfighting the seething sea face to face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trying to prevail by brute force and persistence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At one point, this cruel sea \Nwill mercilessly crush you against the rocks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach is the antipode of the cliff. \NInstead of fighting the cruel sea, the beach plays with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It gently lets the waves roll over,\Nand then turns them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You play pachislot\Nwith a deep feeling of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He already has the bonus flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your demeanor \Nreminds me of myself when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I also had to overcome my hatred at first. \NOnly then the road to the King was revealed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To become a slotter one has to be rich-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One must first overcome his hatred \Nto find the way to the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What could you mean by that? \NSuch an inexplicit guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally writing your own novel? \NWhat's this? Only devised the characters' names so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:50.14,Song,,0,0,0,,Ryo Daiba \NRyo Daiba \NRyo Daiba
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the hero of your last investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could I have heard this name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Double Pachislot-Suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot has already driven someone to suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten years ago, when I myself\Nwas an article writer for a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In one of our interns' articles, \NI happened to see this name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the headline was...\NRight, I remember it:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:21.27,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,800)}"Times" publishing House
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"An elite university student\Ncommits a double pachislot-suicide."
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.34,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(800,900)}Publications Archive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.71,Song,,0,0,0,,An elite university student commits a double pachislot-suicide!! \NWhat was the cause of death? Only we have the key to the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened on the seventh of March.\NFamous student of a prestigious university
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,was found dead in the dormitory of Toto University.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An interesting detail is \Nthat they found him in the pile of electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina Manabu was cuddling \Nhis favourite pachislot machine even after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His best friend Daiba Ryo discovered him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The deceased appeared to have had \Na cardiac arrest due to overworking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No other causes of death were found. \NA subsequent autopsy also found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your best friend die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There must have been something \Ngetting on his nerves lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pachislot! Pachislot was what took the life \Nof my best friend and a promising scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba entered the pachislot world \Nto avenge his best friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the secret\Nbehind the Daiba's God's Finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You play pachislot while hating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my heart, there are no secrets \Nto make me hate pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Teresa, Oumi... Each one of you, albeit in your own fashion, tries to achieve the perfection in pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Win and rise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep winning. You'll see what I'm worth. \NMy path lies to the King's throne!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Contender in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.28,0:22:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Contender in game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NSpark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will \Nstop the time.
